    "body": "Hi all,\n\nI've developed a ping function to send from time to time to avoid disconnection:\n\n    public function Ping()\n    {   \n        $pingHash = array();\n        $pingHash['xmlns'] = \"w:p\";\n        $queryNode = new ProtocolNode(\"ping\", $pingHash, null, null);\n\n        $messageHash = array();\n        $messageHash[\"to\"] = $this->_whatsAppServer;\n        $messageHash[\"type\"] = \"get\";\n        $messageHash[\"id\"] = time().\"-1\";\n        $messageNode = new ProtocolNode(\"iq\", $messageHash, array($queryNode), \"\");\n        $this->sendNode($messageNode);\n    }\n\nI hope this helps.",
